# ggplotpy tests

- Layout: `unit/` (T0), `integration/` (T1), `parity/` (T2), `extensions/`, `gallery/` (T3), `golden/`.
- Register markers in `pyproject.toml`; use `@pytest.mark.needs_*`.
- Optional extensions: **skip with reason**, never fail core CI (D-P009).
- No `@pytest.mark.skip` without comment linking to blocker or D-P009.
- Golden files live in `tests/golden/` — see verification rule for update policy.
- 13-case matrix: `docs/validation_strategy.md`.
